<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Blood-drinking" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Blood-drinking;</orth> 1) preying on the blood: <cit><quote>b. sighs,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.63" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 63</bibl></cit>. 2) bloodthirsty: <cit><quote>my b. hate,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.108" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 108</bibl></cit>. 3) soaked with blood: <cit><quote>in this detested, dark, b. pit,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.224" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 224</bibl></cit>.
